Owlhawk wonders into the room after Kup leaves and
sees the safe.  Getting curious he opens it and
realizes what it contains.  He starts to shour, but
realizes he doesn't want to attract attention so he
points one of his mini-plasma canons on his wrist at
the spark.

Owlhawk:  Goodbye Predico.....(he starts speaking in
Owl's voice as he flinches)  NO HAWK, HE DOESN'T
DESERVE THIS!  HE CAN'T HURT YOU!.....SHUTTUP,
SHUTTUP, I'LL DECIDE WHAT HE DESERVES!.....NO THE
COUNCIL OF ELDERS WILL!.....SHUUUUUTTTTT-UUUUPPPP!

He reaims and fires.

--- RoboRick007 <rfa007@...> wrote:
> ::Hot Rod::
> 
> "Let's not jump the gun here. He may be on a
> mission. Maybe in trouble. But we should be prepared
> to except new command. I'm going to the bridge, to
> see if anything is going on."
> 
> Hot Rod heads towards the ships bridge.
> 
> ::Kup::
> 
> Kup places the spark of DrillBit into a special
> safe, where it will be maintained. He looks over the
> other bots that were destroyed in the explosion. 
> 
> "Well the body of that one Pred(DrillBit) willbe
> usefull if one of our guys gets damaged."
> 
> He looks over the other bodies and recognizes one.
> 
> "No! That Predacon, that was Arcee! I should tell
> Rody!"
> 
> Kup goes off to find Hot Rod.
>
